is who stole the show.

623
00:37:35,920 --> 00:37:38,250
The Fengliu Shop is so eager
to control me.

624
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,820
Sending Madam Bai wasn't enough?

625
00:37:41,280 --> 00:37:42,990
