637
00:38:02,480 --> 00:38:03,950
He's likely already seen through

638
00:38:03,950 --> 00:38:05,750
every one of your foolish moves.

639
00:38:06,800 --> 00:38:08,320
Master is already on his way.

640
00:38:08,320 --> 00:38:10,450
If you still can't think of something,

641
00:38:10,810 --> 00:38:12,120
