646
00:38:33,540 --> 00:38:35,270
Tang Lici may be scheming,

647
00:38:36,060 --> 00:38:37,720
but I'm not without a counter.

648
00:38:37,990 --> 00:38:40,730
The one to stand trial the day
after tomorrow won't be Jiang Qingyu.

649
00:38:40,730 --> 00:38:41,960
It will be Tang Lici.

650
00:38:44,190 --> 00:38:45,720
All I need is for your master

651
00:38:45,750 --> 00:38:47,550
